{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/web-apis/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>웹 앱, 웹 사이트 만들 때 사용할 수 있는 모든 객체 유형<br>\n보통 <a href=\"#javascript\">JavaScript</a>와 함께 사용</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"dom-상속-구조\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dom-%EC%83%81%EC%86%8D-%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0\" aria-label=\"dom 상속 구조 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DOM 상속 구조</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[EventTarget] ← [Node] ← [Element] ← [HTMLElement]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[EventTarget] ← [Node] ← [DocumentType] [CharacterData(Text)]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[EventTarget] ← [Window]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"dom-요소-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dom-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"dom 요소 추가 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DOM 요소 추가</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Properties</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">textContent</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Node.textContent = string</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">모든 콘텐츠 (script, style)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">innerHTML</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.innerHTML = htmlString</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">HTML,XML 마크업 → XSS 공격 위험</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">innerText</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.innerText = string</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">hidden 요소 제외 → reflow발생</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Methods</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">appendChild</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Node.appendChild(Node)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">하나의 Node 객체를 자식노드 맨 뒤에 추가 <br /> return 반환</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">append</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.append(Node, String)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">하나 이상의 Node 객체 또는 String 객체를 <br /> 자식노드 맨 뒤에 추가</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">prepend</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.prepend(Node, String)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">하나 이상의 Node 객체 또는 String 객체를 <br /> 자식노드 맨 앞에 추가</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h2 id=\"shadow-dom-만들기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#shadow-dom-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"shadow dom 만들기 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Shadow DOM 만들기</h2>\n<h3>ShadowRoot</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[EventTarget] ← [Node] ← [DocumentFragment] ← [ShadowRoot]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachShadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'open'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Shadow Host : attach한 DOM 요소</li>\n<li>Shadow Tree : Shadow DOM 내부 트리</li>\n<li>Shadow Root : Shadow Tree의 root node</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>host CSS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>성능 향상을 위해 :host CSS 컨테이너 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> shadowRoot <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachShadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'open'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\tshadowRoot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n\t\t&lt;style>\n\t\t\t:host{color:#000}\n\t\t\t:host(.class){color:#000}\n\t\t&lt;/style>\n\t</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>닫힌 루트 <code class=\"language-text\">{mode: 'close'}</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>사용 지양 (보안 기능이 아님)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"사용자-정의-요소-custom-elements-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EC%A0%95%EC%9D%98-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C-custom-elements-api\" aria-label=\"사용자 정의 요소 custom elements api permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사용자 정의 요소 (Custom Elements API)</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>캡슐화, CustomElementRegistry 객체</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">pupup-components.js</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">myPopup</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">HTMLElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">connectedCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">&lt;div>팝업!&lt;/div></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-popup'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> myPopup<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Or 익명 클래스 (anonymous class)</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-popup'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">extends</span> HTMLElement <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">connectedCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">&lt;div>팝업!&lt;/div></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Or Shadow DOM 사용자 정의 요소</span>\ncustomElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'my-popup'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">extends</span> HTMLElement <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\t\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> shadowRoot <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachShadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'open'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t\tshadowRoot<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">&lt;div>팝업!&lt;/div></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">index.html</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>my-popup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>my-popup</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>customElements.define() : 사용자 요소 정의</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">define</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> constructor<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// CustomElementRegistry method</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">name</code> 사용자 정의 요소 이름<br>\n규칙: 소문자 시작, 하이픈 꼭 포함(HTML 요소와 구분하기 위함)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">constructor</code> 생성자 class 객체</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">options</code> 선택사항 <code class=\"language-text\">{extends: \"p\"}</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Constructor (생성자) : 인스턴스 객체 초기화</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Or Shadow DOM 생성</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">constructor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">attachShadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">mode</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'open'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>직접적인 DOM 조작 금지</li>\n<li>항상 <code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> 호출 (부모 생성자 호출 후 <code class=\"language-text\">this</code> 사용 가능)\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> : 상속 받은 부모 클래스(HTMLElement)의 생성자 호출</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">super()</code> 필요한 경우\n<ul>\n<li>내부 상태 초기화</li>\n<li>shadow DOM 생성 시</li>\n<li>이벤트 핸들러 사전 바인딩 시</li>\n<li>재 렌더링 방지용 flag (<code class=\"language-text\">this._initialized=\"flase\"</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>커스텀 요소 수명 주기 (lifecycle callbacks)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>connectedCallback : DOM 첫 렌더, 요소가(<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;my-popup></code>) DOM에 연결될 때마다 호출\n<ul>\n<li>constructor 사용 안할 시 명시하지 않아도 됨</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>attributeChangedCallback : 속성 변경 시 변경된 부분만 업데이트</li>\n<li>disconnectedCallback : 요소가 DOM에 연결 해제 되었을 때마다 호출</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"useragent\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useragent\" aria-label=\"useragent permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>userAgent</h2>\n<h3><code class=\"language-text\">navigator.userAgent</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>브라우저와 운영체제 정보 문자열</li>\n<li>최신 브라우저는 개인정보를 위해 단순화하여 신뢰도 낮음</li>\n<li>표준화 되어있지 않기때문에 세밀한 필터 불가</li>\n<li>디바이스 감지 정도에만 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> isMobile <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">iPhone|iPad|iPod|Android|BlackBerry|Windows CE</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">i</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>userAgent<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3><code class=\"language-text\">navigator.userAgentData</code></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>UA 객체</li>\n<li>최신 브라우저에서만 사용</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"toggleevent-newstate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#toggleevent-newstate\" aria-label=\"toggleevent newstate permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ToggleEvent: newState</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>요소가 전환되는 상태 String</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"windowlocalstorage\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#windowlocalstorage\" aria-label=\"windowlocalstorage permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>window.localStorage</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[EventTarget] ← [Window]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Methods</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">localStorage.setItem(keyName, keyValue)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">string, array 불가</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">localStorage.getItem(keyName)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">키 값(string) 반환, 없으면 null</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">localStorage.removeItem(keyName)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">키 값 제거</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h2 id=\"windowrequestanimationframe-method\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#windowrequestanimationframe-method\" aria-label=\"windowrequestanimationframe method permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>window.requestAnimationFrame() method</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>브라우저가 다음 화면을 그리기 직전 콜백 실행 (브라우저 주사율 기준 보통 60Hz)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>setInterval 과 비교</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n<th align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">requestAnimationFrame</code></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">setInterval</code></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">실행 타이밍</td>\n<td align=\"left\">다음 프레임 직전</td>\n<td align=\"left\">지정한 ms 무조건 실행</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">백그라운드</td>\n<td align=\"left\">자동 일시정지 (효율적)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">계속 실행 (낭비)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">프레임 동기화</td>\n<td align=\"left\">정확히 맞춤 (부드러움)</td>\n<td align=\"left\">어긋날 수 있음</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">중지</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">cancelAnimationFrame(id)</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">clearInterval(id)</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">reqAni</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'px'</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">requestAnimationFrame</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>reqAni<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">// return 시에도 멈춤</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">reqAni</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> setInt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">setInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">parseFloat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">'px'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentLeft <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token function\">clearInterval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>setInt<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 16ms씩 무조건 실행</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"사이즈와-스크롤\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%EC%A6%88%EC%99%80-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A1%A4\" aria-label=\"사이즈와 스크롤 permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사이즈와 스크롤</h2>\n<h3>Window Size</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Properties</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">window.innerWidth</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">window.innerHeight</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">브라우저 메뉴바, 툴바, 스크롤바 제외</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">window.outerWidth</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">window.outerHeight</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">브라우저 메뉴바, 툴바, 스크롤바 포함</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h3>Size</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Properties</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.clientWidth</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">Element.clientHeight</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Element + padding (스크롤 바 생길 시 제외)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.scrollWidth</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">Element.scrollHeight</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">스크롤 영역 밖 모든 콘텐츠 Element + padding (스크롤 바 생길 시 제외)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.offsetWidth</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.offsetHeight</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Element + padding + border (스크롤 바 생길 시 동일)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h3>Margin size</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Window Methods</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.style.marginLeft</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">인라인 스타일로 지정된 값(String) <br /> 예) 20<u>px</u></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">getComputedStyle(Element).marginLeft</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">css 포함 적용된 스타일 값(String)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h3>Scroll</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Properties</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">window.scrollX</code> <code class=\"language-text\">window.scrollY</code> <br /> === <code class=\"language-text\">.pageXOffset</code> <code class=\"language-text\">.pageYOffset</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">스크롤 된 픽셀 수</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.scrollLeft</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">Element.scrollTop</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Element 내부(overflow:auto) scroll 픽셀 수 get, set <br /> 설정(set) <code class=\"language-text\">Element.scrollTop = number</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.offsetLeft</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">HTMLElement.offsetTop</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">부모 position 기준 상대 좌표 <br /> (부모에 position 없을 시 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body></code> 좌표 또는 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;table></code> 좌표)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Methods</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">window(Element).scrollTo(x, y)</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">.scrollTo({top:y, left:x, behavior: '...'})</code> <br /> === <code class=\"language-text\">.scroll()</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">해당 좌표로 스크롤</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">window(Element).scrollBy(x, y)</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">.scrollBy({top:y, left:x, behavior: '...'})</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">현재 좌표 기준으로 해당 좌표만큼 스크롤</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">Element.getBoundingClientRect()</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Element 크기, 위치 정보를 담은 DOMRect 객체 반환 <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">x</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">left</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">y</code> / <code class=\"language-text\">top</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">right</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">bottom</code> <br /> <code class=\"language-text\">width</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">height</code>, : padding 더한 값</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<h4>부모에 position 있어도 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;body></code> Scroll 값(절대 값) 사용할 때:</h4>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">window.scrollY + Element.getBoundingClientRect().top;</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"cookie\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cookie\" aria-label=\"cookie permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cookie</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>key=value 와 option(path, expires) 문자열</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>set</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">setCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> setExpires</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> numericDays <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">Number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>setExpires<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> expireDate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\texpireDate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>expireDate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> numericDays<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\tdocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cookie <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">; expires=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>expireDate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toUTCString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">; path=/; SameSite=Lax; Secure</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">setCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'cookieName'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'cookieValue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">encodeURIComponent</code> <code class=\"language-text\">decodeURIComponent</code></p>\n<ul>\n<li>.cookie 는 HTTP 헤더 통해 전달: Protocol 준수, 데이터로 인해 쿠키 문자열 형식(<code class=\"language-text\">=</code> <code class=\"language-text\">;</code> <code class=\"language-text\">,</code> …) 파괴 방지<br>\nex) name: <code class=\"language-text\">user=NA=;ME;</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">SameSite</code> : 교차 사이트 요청</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">SameSite=Strict;</code> : 도메인 완전히 일치</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">SameSite=Lax;</code> : iframe, AJAX 호츨에는 전송하지 않음 (일반적)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">SameSite=None;</code> : 도메인 달라도 무조건 전송, Secure 속성 설정되어야만 작동</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Secure</code> : HTTPS 연결에만 쿠키 전송</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>get</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">getCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> escapedName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">replace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">([\\.$?*|{}\\(\\)\\[\\]\\\\\\/\\+^])</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'\\\\$1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> nameMatche <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cookie<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">match</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RegExp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token string\">\"(?:^|; )\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> escapedName <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"=([^;]*)\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> nameMatche <span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token function\">decodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nameMatche<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">$1</code> : 첫 번째 그룹 <code class=\"language-text\">(...)</code> 에서 매치된 텍스트 그대로 치환 <br/>\nex) * → /* (Escape)</li>\n<li>escaped 이유: 정규 표현식 정확히(특수 기호 일반 문자열로 변경) 매칭 <br>\nex) name: <code class=\"language-text\">user.name</code> 일 경우 (패턴 <code class=\"language-text\">.</code>: 모든 문자 1개 매칭) → <code class=\"language-text\">user_name</code> <code class=\"language-text\">user*name</code> 매칭</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>delete</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">deleteCookie</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> initDate <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:00 GMT\"</span>\n\tdocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>cookie <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span><span class=\"token function\">encodeURIComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">=; expires=</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>initDate<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">; path=/; SameSite=Lax; Secure</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>유닉스 타임(Unix Epoch) 시작점</li>\n<li>setCookie 와 option 동일하게 지정</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"geolocation-api\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#geolocation-api\" aria-label=\"geolocation api permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Geolocation API</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>현재 위치 가져오는 API (HTTPS에서만 사용 가능)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">succeess</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">coords</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\tcoords<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>latitude     <span class=\"token comment\">//위도</span>\n\tcoords<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>longitude    <span class=\"token comment\">//경도</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\nnavigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>geolocation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getCurrentPosition</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>success<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"javascript\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javascript\" aria-label=\"javascript permalink\" class=\"link-headers before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JavaScript</h2>\n<h3>JSON</h3>\n<div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Methods</th>\n<th align=\"left\"> </th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">JSON.stringify()</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">Object, array → JSON String</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><code class=\"language-text\">JSON.parse()</code></td>\n<td align=\"left\">JSON String → Object, array</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n<hr>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/ko/docs/Web/API/Web_components/Using_custom_elements\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">사용자 정의 요소</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://web.dev/articles/shadowdom-v1?hl=ko\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://web.dev/articles/shadowdom-v1?hl=ko</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Web APIs","summary":"DOM 요소, Javascript","date":"2025.11.26","categories":["Web Fundamentals"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#e8e8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/bd088/web-apis.png","srcSet":"/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/839df/web-apis.png 192w,\n/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/9f2f3/web-apis.png 384w,\n/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/bd088/web-apis.png 768w","sizes":"(min-width: 768px) 768px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/9f676/web-apis.webp 192w,\n/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/2bb30/web-apis.webp 384w,\n/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/c0224/web-apis.webp 768w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 768px) 768px, 100vw"}]},"width":768,"height":432}},"publicURL":"/static/06535d683e7b474a42be0623db2c0ab0/web-apis.png"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/web-apis/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1463137677"],"slicesMap":{}}